# Pew dbt documentation overlay

Extends [agent-documentation](agent-documentation.mdc) for Pew Digital Data Mart (`ddm-dbt`).

## Doc conventions

- **`CURRENT.md`** is a stable orientation index — not for sprint notes or task tracking.
- ADR template: `docs/decisions/README.md`

## Doc locations

| Purpose | Path |
|---------|------|
| Orientation | `CURRENT.md` |
| Repo map | `docs/repo-map.md` |
| Metrics | `docs/metrics/` |
| Runbooks | `docs/runbooks/` |
| Dashboards | `docs/dashboards/` |
| Operations | `docs/operations/` |
| Templates | `templates/` |
| Decisions | `docs/decisions/` |

## Pew-specific doc context

- GA4 / content metrics: `ga4-metrics.mdc`
- Dashboard consumers: `dashboard-support.mdc`
- Do not add sprint-level notes to `CURRENT.md`.
